alerts.description:
There is a risk of wind gusts (level 1 of 4).
Max. gusts: < 60 km/h; Wind direction: south-west

There is a risk of violent storm gusts (Level 3 of 4).
Height range: > 1000 m; Max. gusts: 90-110 km/h; Wind direction: south-west; Increased gusts: in exposed locations < 130 km/h

There is a risk of gale-force gusts (Level 2 of 4).
Height range: > 600 m; Max. gusts: < 70 km/h; Wind direction: south-west; Increased gusts: in exposed locations < 80 km/h

There is a risk of persistent rain (Level 2 of 4).
Precipitation amounts: ~ 30 l/m²; in windward areas: < 50 l/m²
